title: Garmin MobilePC v5.00.60 Special
description:
Garmin MobilePC 5.00.60 Special version

This modified executable will let you use MobilePC with _all_ your Garmin USB GPS -s via USB, you don't have to buy GPS 10x or GPS 20x anymore!

(Tested with: 60CSx, VistaCx)



Instructions for use:

1. Install MobilePC 5.00.60 (get it from Garmin's website: http://www8.garmin.com/support/collection.jsp?product=010-00685-00 )

2. Replace Que.exe
